Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的行人没有想平常那样推辞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有面红耳赤地流鼻血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为一直都受到铃的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔我也得做些让小铃感到高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下面一起泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这热水一点都不热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  就算水一点都不热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心里却感觉热乎乎的非常温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好澡堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等 睡糊涂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是浴室  是水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和行人一起的话  连心里都热乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说些听不明白的梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点醒来  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,透明  透明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:03:01.97,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了…去取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡糊涂了在水缸中待了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呆看着她也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能去取一些敷在头上降温用的冰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这没有电  没有冰箱的岛上会有冰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能小看自然的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰这东西岛上当然是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的  好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后一道工序在上面加上许多甜的蜂蜜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这种冰透的感觉真让人无法抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这边没有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么 这么突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱  果然你就是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你和雪乃一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是雪乃的姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  妈妈在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雪乃的妈妈 镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我小镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么小镜啊  擅自把熊熊和鸭鸭带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可都是有工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想稍微吃点冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才让熊熊它们陪我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  明明上岁数了  还吃什么刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  谁上岁数了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会上岁数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间的话不一起来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃感冒发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐感冒了?  真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像那种平时越健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发生什么就越脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说柔能克刚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,越坚硬越容易折断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说些不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是来为了取做冰敷用的冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实从奶奶那里听说保管在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有这样的洞窟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是岛上最凉爽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合保管冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上草席  为使它不太容易融化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才和熊熊们把它作成刨冰当点心吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算收下已经添上蜂蜜的冰也没用吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有这么点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿回去的时候就已经融化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  等等  停下  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有其他有冰的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能去山里取了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山?  山是指哪里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山啊  在岛上正中最大的山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顶上不是积了许多雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里把大量的雪取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再压成冰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那快点去取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想快点把冰拿给铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是不错的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是非常辛苦  做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就不用来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  只留下我一个人  真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就算来也是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你带我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不老老实实把我带去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你害羞的过去全部暴露给行人啊  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必与我们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  镜与外表不同其实是非常容易暴躁的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来雪乃害羞的过去是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个有许多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然仙贝不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这种热天有刨冰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说了别用这种方式叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能去稍微取些冰来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有和大家一起出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  到了山顶大家一起打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吧 我们不是特意去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说是因为小铃感冒发烧了去取冰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃居然感冒了  真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋带断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且连黑猫都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多么的不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只不过是迷信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之得快点去取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见麻知  我得快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  姐姐大人  真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小事自己去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  下面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,あ「a」…い「i」…う「u」…え「e」…お「o」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个难道是从麻知姐那得到的叫摩尔斯信号的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰…的…话…行…人…大…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去…富…士…山…取…了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是完美的解读了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近的话直接和我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那么着急的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下要吃不消了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且到了山顶还要打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有还有  要做冰窟在里面吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉能理解雪乃为什么那么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈那么孩子气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说了吧  很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和外面的温差很大  所以会感觉到格外寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有寒冷症  特别怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳落山后会更加冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会放弃的  小铃在等着用冰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃和镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说在这大雪中走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里最暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山顶就在前面  先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗  雪乃也像这样去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的雪  要乘两人飞翔是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  鹰鹰是妈妈优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰鹰是妈妈的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只要是妈妈的请求就不会拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  打中行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  大家快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是山顶  快点开始打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么大的雪中  为什么那人还那么有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记我们的目的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把雪带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然扔到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是雪的话  没必要要来山顶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但山顶还有好风景欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过全是雪什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  行人要是早点说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别反向我发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  不是我的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小铃因感冒而卧床不起  也是机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  在行人取冰回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击熟睡的她  这回一定能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看那样子  现在山顶附近是暴风雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人应该不可能马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遇难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  互相用体温取暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人就这样永远的结合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是理小铃的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纹次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得变大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么点出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行  还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,取冰关键在回程的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算顶上是暴风雪  山下可是盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去时得尽量让雪不能融化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  快看  年糕烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在暴风雪停之前  就算出发也很困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  小铃在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是从刚才开始就没休息过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  这不过这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人嫉妒  为了小铃上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  在这猛烈的暴风雪中勉强下山确实有点危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在冰窟中等风雪停比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  为了小铃得尽快把冰送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和小铃做过这种那种事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  快看  快看  能让鼻血瞬间凝固的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是乱来的话会冻死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩别人的鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我还是要走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就在冰窟里等暴风雪停好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都要把这冰送给小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃  很危险的  就留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  哪里是路完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  小铃更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能认输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:12.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,有急转弯   小心跌落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好天气  那么温暖  感觉想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  一起吃刨冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比比看谁先吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险  这样睡过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  他是男孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  雪乃  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给  酱油味的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不是干这种事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  稍微能躲避一下日晒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃在等着我  得尽快把冰送去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真顽强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰鹰  去帮帮他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  这样下去在到之前就会全部融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕  不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是去了哪里闲逛到现在?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去富士山去取冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这个  已经那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就不是大不了的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡一天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就好了  小铃恢复健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那么喜欢乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在阳光这么强烈的白天去富士山取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为温差太大和过度疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会累倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我又梦到行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和行人一起比赛看谁吃刨冰吃得快的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰没浪费真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看这是行人拿回来的雪块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:12.05,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE7A573}「好吃的 新娘修行」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:34.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我来温暖你…
